import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['date'])]
    
    plt.plot(data['date'], data['disease'], label='Disease Cases', color='blue')
    plt.xlabel('Date')
    plt.ylabel('Disease Cases')
    plt.title('What is the trend of disease cases over time?', wrap=True)
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    plt.legend()
    
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['date'])]
    
    plt.hist(data['wounds'], alpha=0.5, label='Wounds', color='blue')
    plt.hist(data['other'], alpha=0.5, label='Other Injuries', color='green')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of wounds and other injuries?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Number of Injuries')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.legend(loc='upper right')
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['date'])]
    data['month'] = data['date'].dt.strftime('%Y-%m')
    monthly_avg = data.groupby('month')['disease'].mean().reset_index()

    plt.bar(monthly_avg['month'], monthly_avg['disease'])
    plt.xlabel('Month')
    plt.ylabel('Average Disease Cases')
    plt.title('What is the average number of disease cases per month?', wrap=True)
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    plt.legend(['Average Disease Cases'])

    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
